.TH snmpa 3 "snmp 5.20.1" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
snmpa \- Interface Functions to the SNMP toolkit agent

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The module \fIsnmpa\fR contains interface functions to the SNMP agent.

.SH DATA TYPES
.LP
.B
\fBdb() :: volatile | persistent | mnesia.\fR

.br
.RS

