.PP
The send option \fIreceiver\fR specifies where information about delivery of Inform-Requests should be sent. The agent sends Inform-Requests and waits for acknowledgments from the management targets. The \fIreceiver\fR can have three values:

no_receiver
.RS 2
No information is delivered.


.RE
notification_delivery_info/0
.RS 2
The information is delivered via a function call according to this data.


.RE
{tag(), tag_receiver()}
.RS 2
The information is delivered either via messages or via a function call according to the value of 
\fItag_receiver()\fR.
.PP
Delivery is done differently depending on the value of \fItag_receiver()\fR:

pid() | registered_name()
.RS 2
The info will be delivered in the following messages:


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
